{"tid":1688030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泛民維園選舉集會 3名區議會候選人被捕","createTime":"2019-11-02T09:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T16:35:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6a01d5af0080a93e55515a3b8682e6fa999f2da4","tid":1688030,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T09:02:20.000Z","msg":"原定今日舉行的維園集會被警方反對後，逾130名民主派區議會選舉候選人擬今午在維園各自舉行「選舉聚會」。<br />\n<br />\n【16:52】多名區議會候選人與警方理論，其後3名候選人陳振哲、鄭仲恒及文念志被捕。<br />\n<br />\n鄭仲恒是區議會選舉沙田區鞍泰選區候選人，同區候選人還包括招文亮及湯子霈。陳振哲是區議會選舉大埔區林村谷選區候選人，同區另一候選人為陳灶良。文念志是區議會選舉大埔區頌汀選區候選人，同區另一候選人為譚榮勳。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191102/s00001/1572675971773/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191102%2Fs00001%2F1572675971773%2F&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=a94b7b95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191102%2Fs00001%2F1572675971773%2F&h=463470b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191102/s00001/1572675971773/</a>"},{"pid":"f49ca67c647eaff71628729e6fa162c12a1f2d9e","tid":1688030,"uid":14244,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"popo公然違反選舉條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bff6a1f9cd45ad1792aa32140596e8cd56cb254","tid":1688030,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T09:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2b1f4a5e319d2ce178b6be7099b3ff346becab","tid":1688030,"ui